      <text xml:space="preserve">SWIG is a software development tool that connects programs written in C and C++ with a variety of high-level programming languages. SWIG is used with different types of languages including common scripting languages such as Perl, Python and Ruby. For more information see the [http://www.swig.org/ SWIG Website].

BioLib only allows a limited number of SWIG [[supported data types]].</text>
